Table 1. Crystal data and structure refinement for 1 and 2

| Compound | 1 | 2 |
|----------|---|---|
| Empirical formula | C24H16O14Sm2 | C24H16O14Eu2 |
| Formula weight | 829.07 | 832.29 |
| T (K) | 293(2) | 293(2) |
| Wavelength (Å) | 0.71073 | 0.71073 |
| Crystal system | Monoclinic | Monoclinic |
| Space group | P21/n | P21/n |
| Unit cell dimensions |  |  |
| a (Å) | 13.362(4) | 13.316(4) |
| b (Å) | 14.475(3) | 14.437(3) |
| c (Å) | 13.568(2) | 13.540(2) |
| α (°) | 90 | 90 |
| β (°) | 104.058(9) | 103.956(9) |
| γ (°) | 90 | 90 |
| Volume (Å³) | 2545.7(10) | 2526.1(10) |
| Z | 4 | 4 |
| Density (calculated) (g/cm³) | 2.163 | 2.188 |
| Abs. coeff (mm⁻¹) | 4.642 | 4.994 |
| F(000) | 1584 | 1592 |
| Crystal size | 0.32×0.20×0.18 mm³ | 0.36×0.28×0.24 mm³ |
| θ range for data collection | 3.40–23.25° | 3.43–23.21° |
| Index ranges | −14≤h≤14 −14≤k≤15 −15≤l≤12 | −14≤h≤14 −15≤k≤15 −14≤l≤14 |
| Reflections collected | 10292 | 9940 |
| Independent reflections | 3479 [R(int)=0.0283] | 3500 [R(int)=0.0575] |
| Absorption correction | None | None |
| Refinement method | Full-matrix least-squares on F² | Full-matrix least-squares on F² |
| Data/restraints/parameters | 3479/0/362 | 3500/0/362 |
| Goodness-of-fit on F² | 1.127 | 1.316 |
| Final R indices [I>2sigma(I)] | R₁=0.0237 wR₂=0.0587 | R₁=0.0373 wR₂=0.1184 |
| R indices (all data) | R₁=0.0252 wR₂=0.0596 | R₁=0.0420 wR₂=0.1203 |
| Largest diff. peak and hole | 0.633 and −0.803eÅ⁻³ | 0.753 and −1.654eÅ⁻³ |
